Class StepBackSupportedSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator.DecoratorSimulator

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ISimulator

    public class StepBackSupportedSimulator
extends DecoratorSimulator
    This class is intended to be extended by classes which provide functionality to take steps back, according to Decorator pattern
